WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.410 align:middle line:90%
[RELAXING MUSIC]

00:00:00.410 --> 00:00:01.230 align:middle line:90%
[HEART BEATING]

00:00:01.230 --> 00:00:04.190 align:middle line:84%
>> Sometimes, we have
an inner knowing,

00:00:04.190 --> 00:00:07.550 align:middle line:84%
a sense of clarity
that just feels right.

00:00:07.550 --> 00:00:12.140 align:middle line:84%
It is often just a delicate,
quiet, or easy feeling

00:00:12.140 --> 00:00:15.170 align:middle line:84%
that offers direct
perception, answers

00:00:15.170 --> 00:00:18.320 align:middle line:84%
that seem to come, at
times, out of nowhere,

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:22.790 align:middle line:84%
or a very tangible feeling about
what you should or should not

00:00:22.790 --> 00:00:23.690 align:middle line:90%
do.

00:00:23.690 --> 00:00:27.980 align:middle line:84%
In essence, this is what many
people call their intuition.

00:00:27.980 --> 00:00:31.910 align:middle line:84%
These intuitive feelings show
up in most people's lives

00:00:31.910 --> 00:00:36.140 align:middle line:84%
from time to time, random
events that we remember

00:00:36.140 --> 00:00:38.085 align:middle line:90%
as special in some way.

00:00:38.085 --> 00:00:39.420 align:middle line:90%
[RAIN FALLING]

