be so random and fleeting?

00:00:49.160 --> 00:00:51.830 align:middle line:84%
What if we could make
practical intuition

00:00:51.830 --> 00:00:55.580 align:middle line:84%
a normal part of our lives,
something that we can access

00:00:55.580 --> 00:00:58.370 align:middle line:90%
more often and more easily?

00:00:58.370 --> 00:01:00.740 align:middle line:90%
With a little practice, we can.

00:01:00.740 --> 00:01:05.750 align:middle line:84%
Heart intelligence, heart
coherence, and intuition

00:01:05.750 --> 00:01:07.780 align:middle line:90%
are linked and work together.

00:01:07.780 --> 00:01:10.670 align:middle line:84%
Practicing to increase
heart coherence

00:01:10.670 --> 00:01:13.490 align:middle line:84%
a few minutes,
several times a day,

00:01:13.490 --> 00:01:16.250 align:middle line:84%
can help you to be more
intuitive at choice

00:01:16.250 --> 00:01:21.260 align:middle line:84%
points, helping you to choose
your actions and reactions,

00:01:21.260 --> 00:01:25.250 align:middle line:84%
rather than mechanically
respond in the same old

00:01:25.250 --> 00:01:28.380 align:middle line:84%
stress-producing
behavior patterns.

00:01:28.380 --> 00:01:31.200 align:middle line:84%
Here are some
practical situations

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:35.070 align:middle line:84%
where accessing heart
intuition can be very helpful--

00:01:35.070 --> 00:01:37.560 align:middle line:84%
when you have a big
decision to make,

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:39.960 align:middle line:84%
or you are having a
hard time figuring out

00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:43.470 align:middle line:84%
something, increasing
your capacity

00:01:43.470 --> 00:01:47.940 align:middle line:84%
for discerning direction
in sensitive situations,

00:01:47.940 --> 00:01:51.090 align:middle line:84%
deciding when it is
time to speak up,

00:01:51.090 --> 00:01:55.830 align:middle line:84%
or when it is time to hold back,
determining what attitude you

00:01:55.830 --> 00:01:58.830 align:middle line:84%
should bring to a
particular situation,

00:01:58.830 --> 00:02:01.950 align:middle line:84%
detecting when life
is feeding back to us

00:02:01.950 --> 00:02:04.470 align:middle line:84%
that we need to
change an attitude

00:02:04.470 --> 00:02:08.995 align:middle line:84%
or disposition, to help guide
your diet and health choices.

00:02:08.995 --> 00:02:11.550 align:middle line:90%


