00:02:25.410 --> 00:02:27.420 align:middle line:84%
have a set of
leadership competencies,

00:02:27.420 --> 00:02:29.170 align:middle line:90%
intuition is there.

00:02:29.170 --> 00:02:33.870 align:middle line:84%
And I think, we're in a
time in the business world,

00:02:33.870 --> 00:02:37.500 align:middle line:84%
where people are much
more comfortable to talk

00:02:37.500 --> 00:02:41.280 align:middle line:84%
