00:02:59.060 --> 00:03:03.120 align:middle line:84%
>> Here is a tool called the
freeze-frame technique that can

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:07.200 align:middle line:84%
help you access more of your
heart's intuitive intelligence.

00:03:07.200 --> 00:03:11.760 align:middle line:84%
It's a multi-purpose technique
for stopping energy drains

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:14.880 align:middle line:84%
from mentally and emotionally
processing a problem,

00:03:14.880 --> 00:03:18.450 align:middle line:84%
and then gaining clarity
or insight from the heart's

00:03:18.450 --> 00:03:21.555 align:middle line:84%
intuitive guidance as a
more effective approach.

00:03:21.555 --> 00:03:26.260 align:middle line:90%


00:03:26.260 --> 00:03:29.240 align:middle line:84%
It works by shifting
your physiology

00:03:29.240 --> 00:03:34.430 align:middle line:84%
into a coherent state to
synchronize heart and brain,

00:03:34.430 --> 00:03:38.150 align:middle line:84%
then asking yourself questions
to access your heart's

00:03:38.150 --> 00:03:42.470 align:middle line:84%
intuitive guidance,
your heart intelligence.

00:03:42.470 --> 00:03:44.810 align:middle line:84%
For this experience,
I would like

00:03:44.810 --> 00:03:46.970 align:middle line:90%
you to get a pen and paper.

00:03:46.970 --> 00:03:49.770 align:middle line:84%
It will be useful
for this exercise.

00:03:49.770 --> 00:03:51.080 align:middle line:90%
There's no rush.

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.475 align:middle line:90%
Pause the program if needed.

00:03:52.475 --> 00:03:56.230 align:middle line:90%


00:03:56.230 --> 00:04:01.850 align:middle line:84%
OK, I'd like you to think
of a specific situation

00:04:01.850 --> 00:04:06.500 align:middle line:84%
that you feel has been difficult
to solve these past few days.

00:04:06.500 --> 00:04:10.250 align:middle line:84%
Try not to pick the most
emotionally-charged situation

00:04:10.250 --> 00:04:12.680 align:middle line:90%
in your life to start with.

00:04:12.680 --> 00:04:14.570 align:middle line:84%
Pick something where
you'd like to know

00:04:14.570 --> 00:04:19.040 align:middle line:84%
your next steps from your
heart's intuitive guidance.

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:21.420 align:middle line:84%
Write down a few words
about the situation.

00:04:21.420 --> 00:04:30.530 align:middle line:90%


00:04:30.530 --> 00:04:33.290 align:middle line:84%
And under that,
write down how you

00:04:33.290 --> 00:04:35.990 align:middle line:84%
have been mentally and
emotionally feeling

00:04:35.990 --> 00:04:37.190 align:middle line:90%
about the situation.

00:04:37.190 --> 00:04:49.760 align:middle line:90%


00:04:49.760 --> 00:04:53.120 align:middle line:84%
Now, as you have
done before, focus

00:04:53.120 --> 00:04:56.060 align:middle line:90%
on the area around your heart.

00:04:56.060 --> 00:04:58.640 align:middle line:84%
Keep your attention
there as you breathe

00:04:58.640 --> 00:05:01.100 align:middle line:90%
in a comfortable rhythm.

00:05:01.100 --> 00:05:05.090 align:middle line:84%
Imagine your breath is flowing
in and out of your heart area.

00:05:05.090 --> 00:05:14.740 align:middle line:90%


00:05:14.740 --> 00:05:17.680 align:middle line:84%
Make a sincere
attempt to experience

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:21.430 align:middle line:84%
a regenerative feeling,
such as appreciation

00:05:21.430 --> 00:05:26.120 align:middle line:84%
or care for someone or
something in your life.

00:05:26.120 --> 00:05:29.960 align:middle line:84%
Remember, don't try to
simply visualize it,

00:05:29.960 --> 00:05:34.120 align:middle line:84%
but rather to feel it
fully, reexperience it.

00:05:34.120 --> 00:05:42.780 align:middle line:90%


00:05:42.780 --> 00:05:46.500 align:middle line:84%
Now, ask a question
from the heart.

00:05:46.500 --> 00:05:49.230 align:middle line:84%
From this more
objective place, ask

00:05:49.230 --> 00:05:53.490 align:middle line:84%
yourself, what would be a
more efficient or effective

00:05:53.490 --> 00:05:55.335 align:middle line:90%
attitude, action, or solution?

00:05:55.335 --> 00:06:25.470 align:middle line:90%


00:06:25.470 --> 00:06:28.290 align:middle line:84%
Listen to the response
of your heart.

00:06:28.290 --> 00:06:31.860 align:middle line:84%
Quietly observe any subtle
changes in perceptions,

00:06:31.860 --> 00:06:33.285 align:middle line:90%
attitudes, or feelings.

00:06:33.285 --> 00:06:45.110 align:middle line:90%


00:06:45.110 --> 00:06:47.720 align:middle line:84%
Write down what your
heart's intuitive guidance

00:06:47.720 --> 00:06:50.750 align:middle line:84%
offered you, even if
it's just one or two

00:06:50.750 --> 00:06:56.110 align:middle line:84%
words or a simple attitude shift
that your heart is suggesting,

00:06:56.110 --> 00:06:58.140 align:middle line:84%
as this can lead
to new solutions.

00:06:58.140 --> 00:07:05.150 align:middle line:90%


00:07:05.150 --> 00:07:08.840 align:middle line:84%
Commit to sustaining
beneficial attitude shifts

00:07:08.840 --> 00:07:10.170 align:middle line:90%
and acting on new insights.

00:07:10.170 --> 00:07:16.980 align:middle line:90%


00:07:16.980 --> 00:07:21.300 align:middle line:84%
Now, read what you first
wrote down, and then read

00:07:21.300 --> 00:07:26.850 align:middle line:84%
your heart's response,
which is more intelligent.

00:07:26.850 --> 00:07:29.730 align:middle line:84%
We suggest you do the
freeze-frame technique

00:07:29.730 --> 00:07:33.280 align:middle line:84%
in writing until you
get comfortable with it.

00:07:33.280 --> 00:07:36.420 align:middle line:84%
And then you can use it
more casually to help

00:07:36.420 --> 00:07:38.940 align:middle line:84%
you gain the intuitive
discrimination you

00:07:38.940 --> 00:07:42.190 align:middle line:84%
need for making
choices and decisions.

00:07:42.190 --> 00:07:45.060 align:middle line:84%
It will work for you
if you work with it.

00:07:45.060 --> 00:07:48.630 align:middle line:84%
Here are the quick steps
of this technique--

00:07:48.630 --> 00:07:52.950 align:middle line:84%
acknowledge,
heart-focused breathing,

00:07:52.950 --> 00:08:00.560 align:middle line:84%
activate a positive or renewing
feeling, ask, observe and act.

